@startuml
title Diagrama de Comunicación - Gestión de Grupos
actor Admin
participant "GrupoController" as GC
participant "Grupo Model / DB" as GDB
participant "Semestre Model" as SDB
participant "Materia Model" as MDB
participant "Docente Model" as DDB

Admin -> GC: POST /grupos (form)
GC -> SDB: validate semestre_id
GC -> MDB: validate materia_id
GC -> DDB: validate docente_id
GC -> GDB: create grupo
GDB --> GC: grupo
GC --> Admin: redirect grupos.index
@enduml
